caption: Thinking about the past and everything that could be different, if I just listened to my friends about you, but I never did, you were always so nice and I couldn't bring myself to believe what they were saying. You were always loyal and you still are. You'll always be the one that crosses my mind at random times, it's crazy how much I still think about you. #notmyphotography #wishitwas #missingyou #spreadthelove
song_title: I Love You Will Still Sound the Same
